  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reign of the Renegade is a dice-based roguelite deckbuilder. Ascend the tower, brave the odds, and create powerful synergies. Will you end the Reign of the Renegade?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Unique Characters</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Overwhelm enemies as the Warrior, fade into shadows as the Rogue, center yourself as the Monk, or learn and cast spells as the Mage. Each Character has their own arsenal of weapons and unique strengths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Different Classes</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hone each Character's talents further by specializing with Classes. How does your Warrior fight - with the fast-fist-fury of a Berserker, or the exact edge of an Executioner?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>350+ Actions to Master</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Artifacts to Collect</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Enemies to Vanquish</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/27f2169b5ed58caa077b3a7eb33cd9aa.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/27f2169b5ed58caa077b3a7eb33cd9aa.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/27f2169b5ed58caa077b3a7eb33cd9aa.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reign of the Renegade is a dice-based roguelite deckbuilder. Ascend the tower, brave the odds, and create powerful synergies. Will you end the Reign of the Renegade?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Unique Characters</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/191ab78c3eb38a03061af61af92f697e.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Overwhelm enemies as the Warrior, fade into shadows as the Rogue, center yourself as the Monk, or learn and cast spells as the Mage. Each Character has their own arsenal of weapons and unique strengths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Different Classes</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/47fdcfd2c21abe74a3f57015c21bc8b6.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hone each Character's talents further by specializing with Classes. How does your Warrior fight - with the fast-fist-fury of a Berserker, or the exact edge of an Executioner?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>350+ Actions to Master</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/85f70f0e17ae8a376f477d1511a3e3e2.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Artifacts to Collect</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.webm?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/8507b62c0cb5fa10ec042c5030584779.mp4?t=1750955052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Enemies to Vanquish</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306530/extras/27f2169b5ed58caa077b3a7eb33cd9aa.poster.avif?t=1750955052\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/